  • Classes in fi.luupanu.skrapple.logic used by fi.luupanu.skrapple.domain 
    Class and Description
    LetterQueue
    LetterQueue has a set of letters paired with coordinates so that they can then be added to the board.
    LetterQueueValidator
    LetterQueueValidator is the final judge whether or not the LetterQueue is accepted as valid.
    WordChecker
    WordChecker checks if the to-be-added words actually form something meaningful using a Dictionary.
    WordCreator
    WordCreator takes letters from the LetterQueue and tries to form a word or multiple words based on their respectful positions.
